acing=\"0\" class=\"Table_Skeleton\" style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n	<tr>\r\n		<td colspan=\"2\">\r\n		<h3 class=\"Heading2\">First semester</h3>\r\n		</td>\r\n	</tr>\r\n	<tr>\r\n		<td style=\"text-align: left;\">\r\n		<h3 class=\"Heading3\">Unique number: 719268</h3>\r\n		</td>\r\n		<td style=\"text-align: right;\">\r\n		<h3 class=\"Heading3\">Due date: 9 February 2016</h3>\r\n		</td>\r\n	</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n<h3 class=\"Heading3\">Question 3</h3>\r\n\r\n<p><span class=\"BodyText\">The correct mathematical expression for</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span class=\"BodyText\">&quot;a number increased by <span class=\"math-tex\">\\(4\\)</span> less than twice the number<br>\r\nand then the resulting number tripled&quot;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>is:</p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n<li><span class=\"Bullet_List_2\"><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(3(x+4-2x)\\)</span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"Bullet_List_2\"><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(3(x+2x-4)\\)</span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"Bullet_List_2\"><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(3x+4-2x\\)</span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"Bullet_List_2\"><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(x+3(2x-4)\\)</span></span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"Table_Skeleton\" style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n	<tr>\r\n		<td colspan=\"2\">\r\n		<h3 class=\"Heading2\">Second semester</h3>\r\n		</td>\r\n	</tr>\r\n	<tr>\r\n		<td style=\"text-align: left;\">\r\n		<h3 class=\"Heading3\">Unique number: 825579</h3>\r\n		</td>\r\n		<td style=\"text-align: right;\">\r\n		<h3 class=\"Heading3\">Due date: 2 August 2016</h3>\r\n		</td>\r\n	</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n<h3 class=\"Heading3\">Question 3</h3>\r\n\r\n<p><span class=\"BodyText\">The description of the mathematical expression</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(\\displaystyle\\frac{1}{2}x+y\\)</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span class=\"BodyText\">in words that is NOT correc