=\"text/html\" width=\"100%\" height=\"800px\"></iframe></div>','',1,1,'2017-10-11 10:04:58','2017-12-15 10:34:38','',NULL),(306,'Assignment','\r\n<h3 class=\"Heading2\">Assignment</h3>\r\n\r\n','',1,1,'2017-10-11 10:04:58','2017-10-11 10:04:58','',NULL),(307,'Information','\r\n<h3 class=\"Heading2\">Assignment information</h3>\r\n\r\n<ul class=\"BodyText\">\r\n<li><span class=\"Bullet_List_2\">The&nbsp;assignment questions following the fractions&nbsp;learning unit&nbsp;contribute towards your semester mark and final mark.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"Bullet_List_2\">All the assignment questions for&nbsp;the relevant topics can be accessed once all the relevant learning units of the topics have been&nbsp;completed.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"Bullet_List_2\">The assignment&nbsp;has to be submitted online via myUnisa.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"Bullet_List_2\">Refer to the tutorial letter&nbsp;for more information about the assignment.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"Bullet_List_2\">The assignment&nbsp;consists of multiple choice questions.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"Bullet_List_2\">When you are done, click the &#39;Proceed&#39;&nbsp;\r\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"{SYSVAR:MEDIA_REL}/653.JPG\" style=\"width: 23px; height: 22px;\">&nbsp;button to<span class=\"Bullet_List_2\">&nbsp;access the assignment questions.</span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n','',1,1,'2017-10-11 10:04:58','2017-10-11 10:04:58','',NULL),(308,'Questions','\r\n<h3 class=\"Heading2\">Compulsory assignment: Assignment 01, Questions 5 and 6</h3>\r\n\r\n<p><span class=\"BodyText\">If you are registered for the first semester, answer the questions for the first semester.<br class=\"BodyText\">\r\nIf you are registered for the second semester, answer the questions for the second semester.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span class=\"BodyText\">Assignment 01 is compulsory and you&nbsp;<span class=\"BodyText\">must</span>&nbsp;submit it on&nbsp;<em class=\"BodyText\">my</em>Unisa. &nbsp;The marks will