odyText\"><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(\\text a\\)</span></span></p>\r\n		</td>\r\n		<td style=\"text-align: center; width: 2%;\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n		<td style=\"width: 30%;\">\r\n		<p><span class=\"BodyText\">proper fractions</span></p>\r\n		</td>\r\n		<td style=\"width: 5%;\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n	</tr>\r\n	<tr>\r\n		<td style=\"text-align: center; width: 13%;\">\r\n		<p><span class=\"BodyText\"><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(\\text 2\\)</span></span></p>\r\n		</td>\r\n		<td style=\"text-align: center; width: 2%;\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n		<td style=\"width: 30%;\">\r\n		<p><span class=\"BodyText\"><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(\\displaystyle\\frac{3}{5}\\text{; }\\displaystyle\\frac{12}{20}\\)</span></span></p>\r\n		</td>\r\n		<td style=\"text-align: center; width: 5%;\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n		<td style=\"text-align: center; width: 13%;\">\r\n		<p><span class=\"BodyText\"><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(\\text b\\)</span></span></p>\r\n		</td>\r\n		<td style=\"text-align: center; width: 2%;\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n		<td style=\"width: 30%;\">\r\n		<p><span class=\"BodyText\">mixed numbers</span></p>\r\n		</td>\r\n		<td style=\"width: 5%;\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n	</tr>\r\n	<tr>\r\n		<td style=\"text-align: center; width: 13%;\">\r\n		<p><span class=\"BodyText\"><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(\\text 3\\)</span></span></p>\r\n		</td>\r\n		<td style=\"text-align: center; width: 2%;\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n		<td style=\"width: 30%;\">\r\n		<p><span class=\"BodyText\"><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(\\displaystyle\\frac{2}{5}\\text{; }\\displaystyle\\frac{5}{2}\\)</span></span></p>\r\n		</td>\r\n		<td style=\"text-align: center; width: 5%;\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n		<td style=\"text-align: center; width: 13%;\">\r\n		<p><span class=\"BodyText\"><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(\\text c\\)</span></span></p>\r\n		</td>\r\n		<td style=\"text-align: center; width: 2%;\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n		<td style=\"width: 30%;\">\r\n		<p><span class=\"BodyText\">equivalent fractions</span></p>\r\n		</td>\r\n		<td style=\"width: 5%;\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n	</tr>\r\n	<tr>\r\n		<td style=\"text-align: center; width: 13%;\">\r\n		<p><span class=\"BodyText\"><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(\\text 4\\)</span></span></p>\r\n		</td>\r\n		<td style=\"text-align: center; width: 2%;\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n		<td style=\"width: 30%;\">\r\n		<p><span class=\"BodyText\"><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(\\displaystyle\\frac{27}{15}\\text{; }\\displaystyle\\frac{4}{3}\\)</span></span></p>\r\n		</td>\r\n		<td style=\"text-align: center; width: 5%;\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n		<td style=\"text-align: center; width: 13%;\">\r\n		<p><span class=\"BodyText\"><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(\\text d\\)</span></span></p>\r\n		</td>\r\n		<td style=\"text-align: center; width: 2%;\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n		<td style=\"width: 30%;\">\r\n		<p><span class=\"BodyText\">reciprocals</span></p>\r\n		</td>\r\n		<td style=\"width: 5%;\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n	</tr>\r\n	<tr>\r\n		<td style=\"text-align: center; width: 13%;\">\r\n		<p><span class=\"BodyText\"><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(\\text 5\\)</span></span></p>\r\n		</td>\r\n		<td style=\"text-align: center; width: 2%;\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n		<td style=\"width: 30%;\">\r\n		<p><span class=\"BodyText\"><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(1\\displaystyle\\frac{1}{3}\\text{; }4\\displaystyle\\frac{8}{9}\\)</span></span></p>\r\n		</td>\r\n		<td style=\"text-align: center; width: 5%;\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n		<td style=\"text-align: center; width: 13%;\">\r\n		<p><span class=\"BodyText\"><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(\\text e\\)</span></span></p>\r\n		</td>\r\n		<td style=\"text-align: center; width: 2%;\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n		<td style=\"width: 30%;\">\r\n		<p><span class=\"BodyText\">improper fractions</span></p>\r\n		</td>\r\n		<td style=\"width: 5%;\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n	</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"Table_Skeleton\" style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n	<tr>\r\n		<td style=\"width: 5%; vertical-align: top;\">\r\n		<p>1.</p>\r\n		</td>\r\n		<td style=\"width: 45%; text-align: left;\">\r\n		<p><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(\\text{1 a}\\\\ \\text{2 c}\\\\ \\text{3 d}\\\\ \\text{4 e}\\\\ \\text{5 b}\\\\\\)</span></p>\r\n		</td>\r\n		<td style=\"width: 5%; vertical-align: top;\">\r\n		<p>2.</p>\r\n		</td>\r\n		<td style=\"text-align: left;\">\r\n		<p><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(\\text{1 b}\\\\ \\text{2 a}\\\\ \\text{3 e}\\\\ \\text{4 c}\\\\ \\text{5 d}\\\\\\)</span></p>\r\n		</td>\r\n	</tr>\r\n	<tr>\r\n		<td style=\"width: 5%; vertical-align: top;\">\r\n		<p>3.</p>\r\n		</td>\r\n		<td style=\"width: 45%; text-align: left;\">\r\n		<p><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(\\text{1 b}\\\\ \\text{2 e}\\\\ \\text{3 a}\\\\ \\text{4 d}\\\\ \\text{5 c}\\\\\\)</span></p>\r\n		</td>\r\n		<td style=\"width: 5%; vertical-align: top;\">\r\n		<p>4.</p>\r\n		</td>\r\n		<td style=\"text-align: left;\">\r\n		<p><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(\\text{1 a}\\\\ \\text{2 e}\\\\ \\text{3 c}\\\\ \\text{4 d}\\\\ \\text{5 b}\\\\\\)</span></p>\r\n		</td>\r\n	</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n<h3 class=\"Heading3\">Question 6</h3>\r\n\r\n<p><span class=\"BodyText\">Consider the fractions:</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(\\displaystyle\\frac{2}{3}\\text{; }\\displaystyle\\frac{3}{5}\\text{; }\\displaystyle\\frac{5}{8}\\text{; }\\displaystyle\\frac{8}{15}\\)</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span class=\"BodyText\">When they are ordered from the least in value to the greatest in value, we get:</span></p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n<li><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(\\displaystyle\\frac{2}{3}\\text{; }\\displaystyle\\frac{3}{5}\\text{; }\\displaystyle\\frac{5}{8}\\text{; }\\displaystyle\\frac{8}{15}\\)</span><br>\r\n&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(\\displaystyle\\frac{8}{15}\\text{; }\\displaystyle\\frac{3}{5}\\text{; }\\displaystyle\\frac{5}{8}\\text{; }\\frac{2}{3}\\)</span><br>\r\n&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(\\displaystyle\\frac{8}{15}\\text{; }\\displaystyle\\frac{5}{8}\\text{; }\\displaystyle\\frac{3}{5}\\text{; }\\displaystyle\\frac{2}{3}\\)</span><br>\r\n&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li><span class=\"Bullet_List_2\"><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(\\displaystyle\\frac{5}{8}\\text{; }\\displaystyle\\frac{3}{5}\\text{; }\\displaystyle\\frac{2}{3}\\text{; }\\displaystyle\\frac{8}{15}\\)</span></span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"Table_Skeleton\" style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n	<tr>\r\n		<td colspan=\"2\">\r\n		<h3 class=\"Heading2\">Second semester</h3>\r\n		</td>\r\n	</tr>\r\n	<tr>\r\n		<td style=\"text-align: left;\">\r\n		<h3 class=\"Heading3\">Unique number: 825579</h3>\r\n		</td>\r\n		<td style=\"text-align: right;\">\r\n		<h3 class=\"Heading3\">Due date: 2 August 2016</h3>\r\n		</td>\r\n	</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n<h3 class=\"Heading3\">Question 5</h3>\r\n\r\n<p><span class=\"BodyText\">Consider the following statements:</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left: 40px;\"><span class=\"Bullet_List_2\">A: The reciprocal of an improper fraction is a proper fraction.<br>\r\nB: The reciprocal of <span class=\"math-tex\">\\(0\\)</span> is <span class=\"math-tex\">\\(1\\)</span>.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span class=\"BodyText\">Which of the following is true?</span></p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n<li><span class=\"Bullet_List_2\">Only A is correct.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"Bullet_List_2\">Only B is correct.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"Bullet_List_2\">Both A and B are correct.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"Bullet_List_2\">Neither A nor B is correct.</span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<h3 class=\"Heading3\">Question 6</h3>\r\n\r\n<p><span class=\"BodyText\">Consider the following statements:</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left: 40px;\"><span class=\"Bullet_List_2\">A: The mixed number <span class=\"math-tex\">\\(8\\displaystyle\\frac{3}{7}\\)</span>&nbsp;written as an improper fraction is <span class=\"math-tex\">\\(\\displaystyle\\frac{24}{7}\\)</span>&nbsp;.<br>\r\nB: The fractions <span class=\"math-tex\">\\(\\displaystyle\\frac{6}{14}\\)</span>,&nbsp;<span class=\"math-te