ver\"><iframe allowtransparency=\"true\" class=\"ckeditorframe\" scrolling=\"yes\" frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://dev.unisaonline.net/e-content/tao-client/show?launch_url=https://dev.unisaonline.net/tao/ltiDeliveryProvider/DeliveryTool/launch/eyJkZWxpdmVyeSI6Imh0dHA6XC9cL3VuaXNhdGVzdDIuY2xvdWRhcHAubmV0XC90YW9cL3VuaXNhLnJkZiNpMTQ2ODQxNDEzMDI4Nzk1MDY5NiJ9\" type=\"text/html\" width=\"100%\" height=\"800px\"></iframe></div>','',1,1,'2017-10-11 10:04:59','2017-12-15 10:34:40','',NULL),(354,'Information','\r\n<h3 class=\"Heading2\">Assignment information</h3>\r\n\r\n<ul class=\"BodyText\">\r\n<li><span class=\"Bullet_List_2\">The&nbsp;assignment questions following the powers learning unit&nbsp;contribute towards your semester mark and final mark.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"Bullet_List_2\">All the assignment questions for&nbsp;the relevant topics can be accessed once all the relevant learning units of the topics have been&nbsp;completed.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"Bullet_List_2\">The assignment&nbsp;has to be submitted online via myUnisa.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"Bullet_List_2\">Refer to the tutorial letter&nbsp;for more information about the assignment.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"Bullet_List_2\">The assignment&nbsp;consists of multiple choice questions.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"Bullet_List_2\">When you are done, click the &#39;Proceed&#39;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"{SYSVAR:MEDIA_REL}/653.JPG\" style=\"width: 23px; height: 22px;\">&nbsp;button to<span class=\"Bullet_List_2\">&nbsp;access the assignment questions.</span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n','',1,1,'2017-10-11 10:04:59','2017-10-11 10:04:59','',NULL),(355,'Questions','\r\n<h3 class=\"Heading2\">Compulsory assignment: Assignment 01, Questions 9&nbsp;and 10</h3>\r\n\r\n<p><span class=\"BodyText\">If you are registered for the first semester, answer the questions for the first semester.<br class=\"BodyText\">\r\nIf you are registered for the second semester, answer the questions for the second semester.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span class=\"BodyText\">Assignment 01 is compulsory and you&nbsp;<span class=\"BodyText\">must</span>&nbsp;submit it on&nbsp;<em class=\"BodyText\">my</em>Unisa. &nbsp;The marks will contribute towards&nbsp;your semester mark. &nbsp;You have to obtain the answers for all ten&nbsp;questions of Assignment 01 before you&nbsp;submit Assignment 01 on&nbsp;<em class=\"BodyText\">my</em>Unisa.<br>\r\nTherefore, you have to complete all the study units applicable to&nbsp;Assignment 01 before you can submit it.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span class=\"BodyText\">If possible, print this page so that you do not need to go through the whole study unit again to get to&nbsp;the questions.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"Table_Skeleton\" style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n	<tr>\r\n		<td colspan=\"2\">\r\n		<h3 class=\"Heading2\">First semester</h3>\r\n		</td>\r\n	</tr>\r\n	<tr>\r\n		<td style=\"text-align: left;\">\r\n		<h3 class=\"Heading3\">Unique number: 719268</h3>\r\n		</td>\r\n		<td style=\"text-align: right;\">\r\n		<h3 class=\"Heading3\">Due date: 9 February 2016</h3>\r\n		</td>\r\n	</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n<h3 class=\"Heading3\">Question 9</h3>\r\n\r\n<p><span class=\"BodyText\">Consider the following equations:</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left: 40px;\">A: &nbsp;<span class=\"math-tex\">\\((2+3)^3=2^3+3^3\\)</span><br>\r\nB: &nbsp;<span class=\"math-tex\">\\(2^3 \\times 3^3=6^3\\)</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span class=\"BodyText\">Which of the following is true?</span></p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n<li><span class=\"Bullet_List_2\">Only A is correct.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"Bullet_List_2\">Only B is correct.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"Bullet_List_2\">Both A and B are correct.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"Bullet_List_2\">Neither A nor B is correct.</span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<h3 class=\"Heading3\">Question 10</h3>\r\n\r\n<p><span class=\"BodyText\">The expression that is NOT equal to</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(m^5n^3\\)</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>is:</p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n<li><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(\\displaystyle\\frac{n^2m^5}{n^{-1}}\\)</span><br>\r\n&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(\\displaystyle\\frac{(nm)^5}{n^2}\\)</span><br>\r\n&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(\\displaystyle\\frac{1}{m^{-5}n^{-3}}\\)</span><br>\r\n&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(\\displaystyle\\frac{(nm)^3}{m^2}\\)</span><br>\r\n&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"Table_Skeleton\" style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n	<tr>\r\n		<td colspan=\"2\">\r\n		<h3 class=\"Heading2\">Second semester</h3>\r\n		</td>\r\n	</tr>\r\n	<tr>\r\n		<td style=\"text-align: left;\">\r\n		<h3 class=\"Heading3\">Unique number: 825579</h3>\r\n		</td>\r\n		<td style=\"text-align: right;\">\r\n		<h3 class=\"Heading3\">Due date: 2 August 2016</h3>\r\n		</td>\r\n	</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n<h3 class=\"Heading3\">Question 9</h3>\r\n\r\n<p><span class=\"BodyText\">Simplifying the expression </span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(\\displaystyle\\frac{(3x^3)^2}{9x^3}\\)</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span class=\"BodyText\">gives:</span></p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n<li><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(\\displaystyle\\frac{2x^2}{3}\\)</span><br>\r\n&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(x^2\\)</span><br>\r\n&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(\\displaystyle\\frac{2x^3}{3}\\)</span><br>\r\n&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(x^3\\)</span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<h3 class=\"Heading3\">Question 10</h3>\r\n\r\n<p><span class=\"BodyText\">The expression that is NOT equal to</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(p^8q^{-2}\\)</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span class=\"BodyText\">is:</span></p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n<li><span class=\"math-tex\">\\((p^{-4}