ss=\"Bullet_List_2\">Refer to the tutorial letter&nbsp;for more information about the assignment.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"Bullet_List_2\">The assignment&nbsp;consists of multiple choice questions.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"Bullet_List_2\">When you are done, click the &#39;Proceed&#39; \r\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"{SYSVAR:MEDIA_REL}/653.JPG\" style=\"width: 23px; height: 22px;\">&nbsp;button to<span class=\"Bullet_List_2\">&nbsp;access the assignment questions.</span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n','',1,1,'2017-10-11 10:04:59','2017-10-11 10:04:59','',NULL),(441,'Questions','\r\n<h3 class=\"Heading2\">Assignment 03, Questions 1, 2, 3&nbsp;and 4</h3>\r\n\r\n<p><span class=\"BodyText\">If you are registered for the first semester, answer the questions for the first semester.<br class=\"BodyText\">\r\nIf you are registered for the second semester, answer the questions for the second semester.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span class=\"BodyText\">Submit Assignment 03&nbsp;on&nbsp;<em class=\"BodyText\">my</em>Unisa. &nbsp;The marks will contribute towards&nbsp;your semester mark. &nbsp;You have to obtain the answers for all eight&nbsp;questions of Assignment 03&nbsp;before you&nbsp;submit Assignment 03&nbsp;on&nbsp;<em class=\"BodyText\">my</em>Unisa. &nbsp;Therefore, you have to complete all the study units applicable to&nbsp;Assignment 03&nbsp;before you can submit it.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span class=\"BodyText\">If possible, print this page so that you do not need to go through the whole study unit again to get to&nbsp;the questions.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"Table_Skeleton\" style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n	<tr>\r\n		<td colspan=\"2\">\r\n		<h3 class=\"Heading2\">First semester</h3>\r\n		</td>\r\n	</tr>\r\n	<tr>\r\n		<td style=\"text-align: left;\">\r\n		<h3 class=\"Heading3\">Unique number:&nbsp;<span class=\"BodyText\">677160</span></h3>\r\n		</td>\r\n		<td style=\"text-align: right;\">\r\n		<h3 class=\"Heading3\">Due date: 8 March 2016</h3>\r\n		</td>\r\n	</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n<p><span class=\"BodyText\">Questions 1, 2, 3 and 4 are based on the following information:<br>\r\nThe table below gives the prices and quantities of three brands of washing powder sold by Wishy Washy&nbsp;Manufacturing for the years 2010 and 2013.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"Table_Style1\" style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n<thead>\r\n	<tr>\r\n		<th colspan=\"3\" rowspan=\"1\" scope=\"col\"><span class=\"BodyText\">Brands</span></th>\r\n		<th colspan=\"6\" rowspan=\"1\" scope=\"col\"><span class=\"BodyText\">Price per&nbsp;<span class=\"math-tex\">\\(12\\displaystyle\\frac{1}{2}\\:\\text{kg}\\)</span>&nbsp;bag&nbsp;<span class=\"math-tex\">\\((\\Cur)\\)</span></span></th>\r\n		<th colspan=\"6\" rowspan=\"1\" scope=\"col\"><span class=\"BodyText\">Number of&nbsp;<span class=\"math-tex\">\\(12\\frac{1}{2}\\:\\text{kg}\\)</span>&nbsp;bags sold</span></th>\r\n	</tr>\r\n	<tr>\r\n		<th colspan=\"3\" rowspan=\"6\" scope=\"col\">&nbsp;</th>\r\n		<th colspan=\"3\" rowspan=\"6\" scope=\"col\"><span class=\"BodyText\">2010</span></th>\r\n		<th colspan=\"3\" rowspan=\"6\" scope=\"col\"><span class=\"BodyText\">2013</span></th>\r\n		<th colspan=\"3\" scope=\"col\"><span class=\"BodyText\">2010</span></th>\r\n		<th colspan=\"3\" scope=\"col\"><span class=\"BodyText\">2013</span></th>\r\n	</tr>\r\n</thead>\r\n<tbody>\r\n	<tr>\r\n		<td style=\"width: 2%;\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n		<td style=\"width: 15%;\"><span class=\"BodyText\">Ultra Bright</span></td>\r\n		<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n		<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n		<td style=\"text-align: right;\"><span class=\"BodyText\"><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(175\\)</span></span></td>\r\n		<td style=\"width: 6%;\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n		<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n		<td style=\"text-align: right;\"><span class=\"BodyText\"><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(200\\)</span></span></td>\r\n		<td style=\"width: 6%;\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n		<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n