sp;</td>\r\n		<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n		<td style=\"text-align: right;\"><span class=\"BodyText\"><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(10\\Tsp000\\)</span></span></td>\r\n		<td style=\"width: 8%;\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n	</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n<h3 class=\"Heading3\">&nbsp;Question 1</h3>\r\n\r\n<p><span class=\"BodyText\">The simple price index for Econo-wash for 2013 with 2010 as the base year is:</span></p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n<li><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(\\displaystyle\\frac{10\\Tsp000}{8\\Tsp000}\\times100\\)</span><br>\r\n&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(\\displaystyle\\frac{8\\Tsp000}{10\\Tsp000}\\times100\\)</span><br>\r\n&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(\\displaystyle\\frac{150}{130}\\times100\\)</span><br>\r\n&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(\\displaystyle\\frac{130}{150}\\times100\\)</span><br>\r\n<span class=\"Bullet_List_2\">&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<h3 class=\"Heading3\">Question 2</h3>\r\n\r\n<p><span class=\"BodyText\">The composite quantity index for 2013 with 2010 as the base year, rounded to two decimal places, is:</span></p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n<li><span class=\"Bullet_List_2\"><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(87\\Ndp36\\)</span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"Bullet_List_2\"><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(123\\Ndp08\\)</span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"Bullet_List_2\"><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(81\\Ndp25\\)</span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"Bullet_List_2\"><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(114\\Ndp47\\)</span></span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<h3 class=\"Heading3\">Question 3</h3>\r\n\r\n<p><span class=\"BodyText\">The quantity</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(\\displaystyle\\frac{175\\times 6\\Tsp000 + 158 \\times 8\\Tsp000 + 130 \\times 10\\Tsp000}{175\\times 5\\Tsp000 + 158 \\times 6\\Tsp500 + 130 \\times 8\\Tsp000}\\times100\\)</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span class=\"BodyText\">gives:</span></p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n<li><span class=\"Bullet_List_2\">the Paasche price index f