ll be indicated if not clear.</li>\r\n<li>Currency will always be to two decimal places if a decimal value is required.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>?<span class=\"Bullet_List_2\">After completing the assignment questions, proceed to&nbsp;the next&nbsp;learning unit.</span></p>\r\n\r\n','',1,1,'2017-10-11 10:05:00','2017-10-11 10:05:00','',NULL),(535,'page_add_test','\r\n\r\n','',1,1,'2017-10-11 10:05:00','2017-10-11 10:05:00','',NULL),(536,'Toets','\r\n<h3 class=\"Heading2\">Activity</h3>\r\n\r\n<p><span class=\"BodyText\">The prices and quantities sold at William&#39;s Wardrobe for some items of clothing for May 2007 and May 2013 are:</span></p>\r\n\r\n<table border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"1\" cellspacing=\"1\" class=\"Table_Skeleton\" solid=\"\" style=\"width:95%;\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n	<tr>\r\n		<th style=\"width: 20%; text-align: centre;\"><span class=\"BodyText\">Item</span></th>\r\n		<th style=\"text-align: centre;\"><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(\\textrm{Prices in 2007:}\\\\~~~p_{\\,2007}~\\textrm{(R)}\\\\~~\\textrm{(base year)}\\)</span></th>\r\n		<th style=\"text-align: centre;\"><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(\\textrm{Quantities sold in 2007:}\\\\~~~~~~~~~~q_{\\,2007}\\\\~~~~~\\textrm{(base year)}\\)</span></th>\r\n		<th style=\"text-align: centre;\"><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(\\textrm{Prices in 2013:}\\\\~~~p_{\\,2013}~\\textrm{(R)}\\\\~~\\textrm{(given year)}\\)</span></th>\r\n		<th style=\"text-align: centre;\"><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(\\textrm{Quantities sold in 2013:}\\\\~~~~~~~~~~q_{\\,2013}\\\\~~~~~\\textrm{(given year)}\\)</span></th>\r\n	</tr>\r\n	<tr>\r\n		<td><span class=\"BodyText\">Ties (each)</span></td>\r\n		<td><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(~\\,100\\)</span></td>\r\n		<td><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(1\\,000\\)</span></td>\r\n		<td><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(~\\,200\\)</span></td>\r\n		<td><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(900\\)</span></td>\r\n	</tr>\r\n	<tr>\r\n		<td><span class=\"BodyText\">Suits (each)</span></td>\r\n		<td><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(1\\,200